{"tid":2195138,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民悼梓樂 警威嚇︰點蠟燭就告","createTime":"2020-09-09T03:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T03:45:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6aefa20dc8de22a87f62ec04c59e5f5ef8d08d","tid":2195138,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/V3H3LG7UAZFQXEWWF5QQYHKWVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FV3H3LG7UAZFQXEWWF5QQYHKWVM%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgxdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=b50692c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FV3H3LG7UAZFQXEWWF5QQYHKWVM%2F&h=12974965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/V3H3LG7UAZFQXEWWF5QQYHKWVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n市民悼梓樂 警威嚇︰點蠟燭就告<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wKtzbqSBBuPYM3eK8hpWl_aKKdc=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A6CRRVWXVRFAZFWU23GUJASDNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwKtzbqSBBuPYM3eK8hpWl_aKKdc%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA6CRRVWXVRFAZFWU23GUJASDNE.jpg&h=51daebfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■市民輪流在祭壇前默哀，現場大批機動部隊人員和傳媒聯絡隊員監視。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】22歲科大學生周梓樂逝世10個月，科大學生會和科大校董會學生代表呼籲市民，昨晚8時9分默哀一分鐘悼念。巿民昨在將軍澳尚德邨停車場外重建小祭壇，悼念周梓樂及15歲女生陳彥霖，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳重兵戒備<br />\n<br />\n小祭壇放置周梓樂及陳彥霖的肖像，並以白蠟燭砌成十字架，昨午開始已有零星市民上前獻花。及至傍晚，警方開始在附近一帶戒備，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其間有市民欲燃點蠟燭時，一名傳媒聯絡隊員上前干涉，以現場燃點太多蠟燭為由叫停，更聲言只要市民燃點蠟燭「你一點放低就告你，你咪試吓囉」。之後一名女巿民移步至祭壇前雙手合十拜祭，喊道：「阿仔阿仔，你真係死得慘咯，有仇報仇，有冤報冤......」原本在她旁邊的警員立即退開。<br />\n<br />\n周梓樂去年11月4日凌晨約1時，在尚德邨停車場三樓離奇墮下二樓，頭部重創昏迷，搶救四日至8日早上8時9分不治。此後每月8日，巿民都在尚德邨停車場外悼念，多次爆發警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g9z5s9cx6thAfWYghCbvA3ZsfnI=/1979x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AZU6GWLIQVGJVICZJ35ZI3GWTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg9z5s9cx6thAfWYghCbvA3ZsfnI%3D%2F1979x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAZU6GWLIQVGJVICZJ35ZI3GWTE.jpg&h=a07edb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■小祭壇放置周梓樂及陳彥霖肖像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8mXO3RK-QlzZDtmDlMtGG84R_tc=/2345x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PS7YH75Z5BDG7MUJQUKA33EFII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8mXO3RK-QlzZDtmDlMtGG84R_tc%3D%2F2345x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPS7YH75Z5BDG7MUJQUKA33EFII.jpg&h=652b236b&s={SIZE}\" />                               <br />\n■一名傳媒聯絡隊員與致祭市民齟齬。"}]}